body:
• Added search bar (which can be disabled)!;
• Song item layout changes;
• Other minor changes/fixes;

As per users request:
• Return to Raleway + Roboto condensed;
• Partially reverted to the old design;
• Reverted to the previous accents (!because of the color resources changes You have to set the theme again after the update!);
Other:
• Minor theme changes;

- UI refinements;
- Add stroke to selected album;
- New typeface (OpenSans);
- New accents;
- Fixes;
- Migrate to AndroidX;
- Replace Loader with ViewModel;

- New rounded icons style!;
- Dynamic shuffle button: randomly plays the artist or the device songs;
- UI review;
- Restore albums/songs list initial position when a new artist is selected;
- Fix expand button rotate animation;

New UI!
- The controls are now fixed at the bottom of the screen and they contains equalizer, player ui and the settings button;
- Top panel containing the now played song. By clicking on it you can 'reveal' the selected artist's discography;
- Other UI changes;

- Added a floating button to play all songs in device, and added a click
feedback on artist (in artist panel) to play all its songs;
- Fix sliding panel freezes when, during its expansion, the view below is touched;
- Show explanation of the options by long clicking on them;
- Close settings when a song is selected;
- Use normal ripple when clicking on albums, artists and songs;
